            </div>

            <div class="info">
                <strong>🗺️ LONG-TERM ROADMAP (2025-2026)</strong><br>
                • <strong>Q4 2025:</strong> Enhanced AI interactions, community features<br>
                • <strong>Q1 2026:</strong> Battle system, breeding mechanics<br>
                • <strong>Q2 2026:</strong> Mobile app launch (iOS/Android)<br>
                • <strong>Q3 2026:</strong> Developer API and third-party integrations<br>
